title: CRED REA Fish Team Belt Transect Surveys at Laysan Island, 2002
name: cred-rea-fish-team-belt-transect-surveys-at-laysan-island-2002
notes: Belt transects along 3 consecutively-placed, 25m transect lines were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 3 sites at Laysan Island in September, 2002 NOAA vessel Townsend Cromwell (TC02-07). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
